        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain, then chop your <strong>king prawns</strong> until they are very finely minced (keep chopping until they become sticky!)</p><p>Combine the <strong>minced</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and your <strong>soy sauce </strong>– this is your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawn toast mix</strong></p>",
