    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine most of your <strong>mayo </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>to<strong> </strong>a separate bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1681478903533-x200.jpg",
