            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, spread the <strong>remaining mayo </strong>over the top of your <strong>ciabatta lid[s]</strong> and sprinkle over your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>ciabatta lid[s] </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 or until the ciabatta is starting to brown – this is your <strong>sesame ciabatta lid</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
