          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>king prawn</strong> <strong>toast</strong> with a dollop of <strong>sriracha mayo</strong>, some <strong>quick-pickled slaw </strong>and the <strong>sesame ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>king prawn toast sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawn toast sandwich </strong>with the <strong>fries </strong>and any <strong>remaining quick-pickled slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
